Hudson Hotels to buy 9 hotels for $ 47 mln . Hudson Hotels Corp said Wednesday that it has signed a definitive agreement to acquire nine Hampton Inns from a subsidiary of Equity Inns Inc for $ 47 , 250 , 000 . Hudson Hotels said the nine hotels have annual revenues of about $ 16 million , and will boost its annual revenues to about $ 55 million . They contain a total of 1 , 089 hotel rooms , giving Hudson 41 hotels under management with 4 , 625 rooms . The company also said it will seek to buy more Hampton Inn properties . It said the transaction is subject to final due diligence and specific contract negotiation . Closing is expected prior to October 1 . Hudson Hotels develops and manages hotel properties for its own account , as well as through partnerships and joint ventures . 
